snippet.title: Steins;Gate 0 - Launch Trailer | PS4, PS Vita
snippet.description:
The sequel to the award winning sci-fi visual novel series. Unable to save Makise Kurisu, Okabe has resigned to life in the Beta Worldline and the onset of Word War III - that is, until faced with a ghost from the past, in the form of an artificial intelligence program called Amadeus.

Rated Mature: Blood, Strong Language, Suggestive Themes, Violence

http://steinsgatezero.com
